Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.80,0:20:46.78,IN2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}追いかけていた my precious world
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.78,0:20:51.80,IN2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}魅せてあげる　B.B.
Dialogue: 1,0:18:55.82,0:19:01.65,IN2-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}黑暗之中  只能感受到安静的心跳
Dialogue: 1,0:19:01.65,0:19:07.16,IN2-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}当幕布拉开  已经没有退路
Dialogue: 1,0:19:07.16,0:19:12.75,IN2-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}被封锁的视野  香甜的蜜汁
Dialogue: 1,0:19:12.75,0:19:18.42,IN2-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}这里是虚伪的乐园
Dialogue: 1,0:19:18.42,0:19:24.67,IN2-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}依然能像蛹一般
Dialogue: 1,0:19:24.67,0:19:29.56,IN2-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}处在封闭空间中吗？
Dialogue: 1,0:19:29.56,0:19:34.90,IN2-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}但你也一样吧
Dialogue: 1,0:19:34.90,0:19:40.27,IN2-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5\3c&HEA182B&\t(400,400,\3c&H587AD3&)}当沐浴到耀眼的光芒
Dialogue: 1,0:19:40.27,0:19:42.85,IN2-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}就让我的舞台解放吧
Dialogue: 1,0:19:42.85,0:19:45.66,IN2-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}蝴蝶翅膀闪耀着光辉
Dialogue: 1,0:19:45.66,0:19:51.10,IN2-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}展翅飞翔后  便不会停歇
Dialogue: 1,0:19:51.10,0:19:56.30,IN2-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}用尽整个生命  为你献上歌声
Dialogue: 1,0:19:56.30,0:19:59.36,IN2-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}我不断追寻的美好世界
Dialogue: 1,0:19:59.36,0:20:04.06,IN2-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}会展现在你眼前  Butterfly Bright
Dialogue: 1,0:20:04.06,0:20:09.27,IN2-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}就连泪水  也化作灯火
Dialogue: 1,0:20:09.27,0:20:14.86,IN2-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}为我带来色彩的音阶
Dialogue: 1,0:20:14.86,0:20:18.79,IN2-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}重叠起来  发出光芒
Dialogue: 1,0:20:18.79,0:20:27.27,IN2-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5\t(6300,6500,\3c&HF1DD02&)}又会将他人照亮
Dialogue: 1,0:20:27.27,0:20:30.25,IN2-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5\3c&HF1DD02&\t(1500,2000,\3c&HD704C5&)}现在让我的舞台解放吧
Dialogue: 1,0:20:30.25,0:20:32.99,IN2-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}蝴蝶翅膀闪耀着光辉
Dialogue: 1,0:20:32.99,0:20:38.32,IN2-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}展翅飞翔后  便不会停歇
Dialogue: 1,0:20:38.32,0:20:43.80,IN2-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}用尽整个生命  为你献上歌声
